snippet.title: System Design Course Overview
snippet.description:
You can check out the course here:

https://get.interviewready.io/courses/system-design-interview-prep

This is a set of 4 chapters, which dive into System Design in-depth. The videos also have supplementary content:
1) Capacity Planning
2) API contracts
3) Architecture Diagrams
4) Tests
5) FAQs
6) Subtitles

00:00 Course Target Audience
00:48 What's inside?
02:02 Pricing
02:22 Course Walkthrough
05:15 Future plans
